0-11 14:57:15\"\n    },\n    \"flatsome-child::blog_show_excerpt\": {\n        \"value\": false,\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2023-10-11 14:57:15\"\n    }\n}', '', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5bc3cb62-b9a7-46cf-9ab6-b300e51cf1e0', '', '', '2023-10-11 14:57:15', '2023-10-11 14:57:15', '', 0, 'https://minhhoang04.demopolyct.online/?p=358', 0, 'customize_changeset', '', 0),
